Construction of four additional&nbsp;travel lanes (two in each direction) to approximately&nbsp;5 miles of I-85 from north of&nbsp;Lane Street&nbsp;(Exit 63) to north of&nbsp;NC152 (Exit 68) in&nbsp;Rowan County. The Contractor will need to have&nbsp;nightly lane&nbsp;closures along I-85&nbsp;for&nbsp;construction of the&nbsp;I-85 widening project&nbsp;.
